com.pom.crimson.pages

Class FullImageViewPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.FullImageViewPage

  • public class FullImageViewPage
extends BasePage
    FullI Image View Page opens an image in Moments log in full page view
    User can view images in carousal. Edit, Share image in Group chat or externally via this page. User can navigate to this page by :

    Go to Home Page
    Click "Moments log" widget
    Click "Add new moment" link
    Create a moment with image
    Once moment is created,Tap on moment.

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
